name: Path M
title: LymphomaOcularAdnexa Path M (no UICC definition)
notes:
**Note 1:** Involvement of peripheral and central lymph nodes, distant nodes for ocular adnexal lymphomas, is coded in lymph nodes (N) not distant metastasis (M).

**Note 2:** UICC does not define Lymphoma Ocular Adnexa. A list of all possible Pathologic M values is provided.
